"title": "7416: purification",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7416: purification",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Cleansing from sin or uncleanness, by means of ritual washing under the old covenant, but through the blood of Jesus Christ under the new covenant.</p>\n<h2>Purification from uncleanness</h2>\n<h3>After contact with something unclean</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:39-Lev11:40\">LEV 11:39–11:40</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev15:1-Lev15:12\">LEV 15:1–15:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev15:19-Lev15:23\">LEV 15:19–15:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev17:15-Lev17:16\">LEV 17:15–17:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num19:10-Num19:20\">NUM 19:10–19:20</a></p>\n<h3>After disease</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev15:13-Lev15:15\">LEV 15:13–15:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:1-Lev14:32\">LEV 14:1–14:32</a></p>\n<h3>After childbirth and menstruation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:22\">LUK 2:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev12:1-Lev12:8\">LEV 12:1–12:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:2-2Sam11:4\">2SA 11:2–11:4</a></p>\n<h2>Purification from sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:7\">1JN 1:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num19:1-Num19:9\">NUM 19:1–19:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:5\">JOB 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:3\">HEB 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:16-Heb9:24\">HEB 9:16–9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:9\">1JN 1:9</a></p>\n<h2>Purification of people</h2>\n<h3>Priests and Levites</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:20\">EZR 6:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:18-Exod30:21\">EXO 30:18–30:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:24-Lev16:28\">LEV 16:24–16:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:5-Num8:22\">NUM 8:5–8:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num19:7\">NUM 19:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:6\">2CH 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:30\">NEH 12:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:22\">NEH 13:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:30\">NEH 13:30</a></p>\n<h3>Lay people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:24-Acts21:26\">ACT 21:24–21:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:1-Gen35:2\">GEN 35:1–35:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num19:20\">NUM 19:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:19\">NUM 31:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:13-2Chr30:20\">2CH 30:13–30:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:17\">ISA 66:17</a></p>\n<h2>Purification of inanimate objects</h2>\n<h3>The temple</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:8\">2CH 34:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:15-2Chr29:19\">2CH 29:15–29:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:6-Neh13:9\">NEH 13:6–13:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:18-Ezek45:20\">EZK 45:18–45:20</a></p>\n<h3>Sacred objects</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:36\">EXO 29:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:15\">LEV 8:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr23:28\">1CH 23:28</a></p>\n<h3>Other items</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:48-Lev14:53\">LEV 14:48–14:53</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:19-Num31:24\">NUM 31:19–31:24</a></p>\n<h2>Purification of precious metals</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps12:6\">PSA 12:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:3\">MAL 3:3</a></p>\n<h2>Purification of the inner person</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:1\">2CO 7:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:2-Mark7:8\">MRK 7:2–7:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:5-Acts15:11\">ACT 15:5–15:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:11-Titus2:14\">TIT 2:11–2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:8\">JAS 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:22\">1PE 1:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:3\">1JN 3:3</a></p>",
